snippet.title: Wee Tanks Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
You can join the discord server (and download and try the game yourself): https://discord.gg/wGNppWf

Wee Tanks is a game I have been working on the last couple of months and is slowly growing to become a full stand-alone game, in this trailer you get a small glimpse of what it currently looks like.

The game is far from finished so what you now will see will probably be different in the future, interested in playing or helping me making this game awesome?? Join the discord server, everyone is welcome.
